         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Why do we think that this is "Purves" ¶  ¶ or "Perry" ¶  ¶ Hodgkinson was still Act/ Comm Lands and Works in 1873 ¶ Have not found 1873 list of civil servants. ¶  ¶ No Purves or Pervis in 1864, in 189...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="Progressnote"
               style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; margin-bottom: 0.0416in; margin-left: -0.8861in; text-indent: 0.8861in; color: #C00000; hyphenate: false; break-before: page; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">Perry?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">nos at top of letter: 73/K6200 -unable to find this letter in VPRS 44/P, unit 750 and it is not on the database.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Why do we think that this is "Purves"<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>or "Perry"<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Hodgkinson was still Act/ Comm Lands and Works in 1873</p>
            <p rend="Progressnote"
               style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; margin-bottom: 0.0416in; margin-left: -0.8861in; text-indent: 0.8861in; color: #C00000; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Have not found 1873 list of civil servants.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="Progressnote"
               style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; margin-bottom: 0.0416in; margin-left: -0.8861in; text-indent: 0.8861in; color: #C00000; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">No Purves or Pervis in 1864, in 1890 a Thos Pervis, but first appointed 1885; and a Robert<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Pervis, at Ballarat Post office, first appointed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1878.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">73.04.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">[Thomas? Purves]</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Unit 4, p. 341, VPRS 7936/P1 outward letterbooks of the Secretary for Lands, VA 538 Department of Crown Lands and Survey, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Office of Lands and Survey,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 9th Apl, 1873.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Honorable The Minister of Lands and Agriculture having directed me to arrange for Mr Ferguson<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>William Ferguson.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to come to Town for the purpose of selecting from the Botanical Gardens such nursery plants as are required to stock the Macedon Nursery, and to instruct you to furnish same, I beg to request that you will inform me on what day it will be convenient for you to meet Mr Ferguson at the Botanical Gardens for such purpose.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedt Servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                    style="font-weight: bold; background-color: #FFFF00; ">[… Purves]</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Assistant<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">Commisioner</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of Lands and Survey.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanical Gardens,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne.</p>
         </div>
